### 5. **ANIMATEIN COMPONENT (Scroll-triggered reveals)**

**Files:** `/root/repos/apex-session-haarlem/src/components/AnimateIn.tsx`

**Pattern:**
- Uses Intersection Observer
- Triggers when element enters viewport
- Staggered animation via `delay` prop
- Direction-based initial state (up/left/right)
- Once: true (animates only once)

**Code:**
```tsx
export default function AnimateIn({
  children, delay = 0, direction = "up",
}: AnimateInProps) {
  const initial = {
    opacity: 0,
    ...(direction === "up" && { y: 40 }),
    ...(direction === "left" && { x: -40 }),
    ...(direction === "right" && { x: 40 }),
  };

  return (
    <motion.div
      initial={initial}
      whileInView={{ opacity: 1, y: 0, x: 0 }}
      viewport={{ once: true, margin: "-60px" }}
      transition={{ duration: 0.8, delay, ease: [0.16, 1, 0.3, 1] }}
    >
      {children}
    </motion.div>
  );
}
```

